name: pymetis
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "PyMetis" %}
{% set version = "2022.1" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: f849e2cb3e49da8e5c82a3e76830fe04175ba2d31bc436898f8dedfe9d6dde9b

build:
  number: 0
  script: |
    {{ PYTHON }} ./configure.py --no-use-shipped-metis --metis-inc-dir=$PREFIX/include --metis-lib-dir=$PREFIX/lib
    {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
    - cross-python_{{ target_platform }}     # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - pybind11
    - python
  host:
    - pip
    - metis
    - pybind11
    - python
  run:
    - python
    - metis
    - six

test:
  imports:
    - pymetis
  requires:
    - pip
    - pytest
    - numpy
    - metis
    - meshpy  # [unix and x86_64]
  source_files:
    - test
  commands:
    - cd test && python -m pytest

about:
  home: https://github.com/inducer/pymetis
  summary: A Graph Partitioning Package
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - inducer
